{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9751eb9040","title":"大字报——无题","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"710ccc2a62","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"9751eb9040"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"860082c4c6","name":"朱承立"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4361ed4768","type":"title","text":"大字报——无题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"2066730488","type":"authors","text":"北京大学朱承立","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"6a34731a5e","type":"paragraph","text":"（朱承立：北京大学西语系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"94860d82aa","type":"paragraph","text":"见民主墙有人作诗反对〈是时候了〉，表面冠冕堂皇，但颇露出某些领导者的心惊肉跳，回诗驳之：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"0eb5c020e1","type":"paragraph","text":"并兼领导同志们，是时候了，是的，是时候了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"bfe260264c","type":"paragraph","text":"是黑暗……角落大放光明的时候了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"8134950a97","type":"paragraph","text":"是兄弟姐妹向层层的高墙坍塌的时候了。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"8e7bcf84cc","type":"paragraph","text":"是老爷的威风扫地的时候了。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"86b5758045","type":"paragraph","text":"是“看风转舵”“吹吹拍拍”“拉拉扯扯”的歪风扫地的时候了，是时候了，是时候了。我们要喊千遍是时候了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"7603237e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"那些背后藏着棍子的人，端端庄庄的，一脸正经说，“为什么‘是时候了’，难道你把党看作国民党？”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"fb361624e1","type":"paragraph","text":"那是打着“教育改造”人的腔调的人，轻松地说“整风嘛，以前也有，不足为奇……客观规律”，……","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"7c08e72214","type":"paragraph","text":"但是","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"73ecd32d81","type":"paragraph","text":"他们的心都在颤抖。“我，我的威信，要垮了，呵，我××要被揭露了。我将来还怎样地领导？”是的，你这样下去。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"a2a535b143","type":"paragraph","text":"主要是“是时候了。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"2afd06c2c3","type":"paragraph","text":"那就是","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"},{"id":"c273aed453","type":"paragraph","text":"你将什么也不能领导。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040"}],"page":{"id":"0ec721bb26","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9751eb9040","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}